---
alwaysApply: true
---

UI is implemented with Dioxus.

Patterns:

- Views are container components.
- Business logic lives in custom hooks.
- Child components are presentation-only.
- Avoid waterfall requests using streams and/or try_join!.

Examples reference:

- use_action
  src/infrastructure/ui/views/login.rs
  src/infrastructure/ui/hooks/login.rs
- use_resource
  src/infrastructure/ui/views/patient_dashboard.rs
  src/infrastructure/ui/hooks/patient_programs.rs
- parallel requests:
  src/application/use_cases/get_patient_programs.rs
  src/application/use_cases/submit_patient_workout_feedback.rs

Dependency injection:

src/infrastructure/app_context.rs acts as a dependency container.
